# Install

#### Clone project
```
git clone https://github.com/ndiing/server.git
```
#### Change directory
```
cd server
```
#### Install packages
```
npm install
```
#### Start server
```
npm start
```
#### Install any update
```
npm update

// and then start again
npm start
```
